            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "...Now do you understand? In the end, everything everyone does will eventually turn out this way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "The more you learn about alchemy, the more disappointment and despair you will experience."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Keith..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I understand your point of view as well. After all, I once felt the same as you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "However, people's malice is massive and dark, and it knows no end. It engulfs everything else..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "To the point that it will engulf its human creator..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I know this may sound weird after what I just said...but you should follow your own path."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Over the course of your own experiences, you may come to a different conclusion."
